    <section class="ftco-section" id="servicesSection">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center mb-5 pb-5">
          <div class="col-md-7 text-center heading-section ftco-animate">
            <h2>Services</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 d-flex align-self-stretch ftco-animate">
            <div class="media block-6 services p-3 py-4 d-block text-center">
              
              <div class="media-body">
                <h3 class="heading">Pet and Owner Registration</h3>
                <p>City Veterinary Office aims to make Marikina City a stray and rabies free city, to do this, City Veterinary Office enforcing pet owners to register themselves and their pet to their office, which is according also to RA 9482 or the THE ANTI RABIES Act. Which states that every pet owners should have their pet dogs and cats to regularly vaccinated against rabies and submit their pet dogs and cats to mandatory registration. </p>
              </div>
            </div>      
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 d-flex align-self-stretch ftco-animate">
            <div class="media block-6 services p-3 py-4 d-block text-center">
              <div class="icon mb-3"></div>
              <div class="media-body">
                <h3 class="heading">Daily Stray Animal Apprehension</h3>
                <p>City Veterinary Office's  main task is to eradicate stray animals to provide protection against the spread of deadly rabies caused by animal bites, particularly dogs and cats and to control excessive breeding of dogs by irresponsible pet owners, causing animals to become stray which poses a health risk to humans. </p>
              </div>
            </div>      
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 d-flex align-self-stretch ftco-animate">
            <div class="media block-6 services p-3 py-4 d-block text-center">
              <div class="icon mb-3"></div>
              <div class="media-body">
                <h3 class="heading">Pet Redemption</h3>
                <p>If you believe that your pet has been impounded as stray animal, City Veterinary Office is gladly informing you that 
                    they let Pet Owners redeem their impounded pet by undergoing redemption process. 
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>    
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 d-flex align-self-stretch ftco-animate">
            <div class="media block-6 services p-3 py-4 d-block text-center">
              <div class="icon mb-3"></div>
              <div class="media-body">
                <h3 class="heading">Pet Adoption</h3>
                <p>City Veterinary Office frantically calling out for people to adopt the dogs currently impounded at the City Veterinary Office (CVO) in Marikina. The dogs will be scheduled to be put to sleep if they are not adopted out soon. Currently, due to the efforts of the group, 14 out of the 42 dogs are now adopted. The group was also able to convince the CVO to temporarily halt the euthanasia of unclaimed dogs.</p>
              </div>
            </div>      
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

 
    

    <section class="ftco-section cover_1" style="background-image: url(/websitePart/images/bg_34.jpg);" data-stellar-background-ratio="0.5" id="faqSection">
      <div class="overlay"></div>
       <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row justify-content-center mb-5 pb-5">
          <div class="col-md-7 text-center heading-section ftco-animate">
            <h2><font color="white">Frequently Asked Question</font></h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row no-gutters ftco-animate">
          <div class="carousel owl-carousel ftco-owl">
           <% faq.forEach(function (i) { %>
            <div class="item text-center">
              <div class="testimony-wrap p-4 pb-5">
               
                <div class="text">
                <p class="name"><%= i.str_Question %></p>
                  <p class="mb-5"><%= i.str_Answer %></p>
            
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <% }); %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


  <section class="ftco-section bg-light" id="animalSection">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center mb-5 pb-5">
        <div class="col-md-7 text-center heading-section ftco-animate">
          <h2>Animals</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 mb-3 text-center ftco-animate">
          <div class="pricing p-4 py-5">
            <div class="icon mb-2"><span class="flaticon-skyline"></span></div>
            <h3 class="mb-3">Redemption</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Lost pet? Find it here.</p>
       
            <p><a href="/CVO_Homepage/Redemption" class="btn btn-primary">View Animals For Redemption</a></p>
            <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="$('#modalRedemptionProcess').modal('toggle');">Instruction</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 mb-3 text-center ftco-animate">
          <div class="pricing p-4 py-5">
            <div class="icon mb-2"><span class="flaticon-skyline"></span></div>
            <h3 class="mb-3">Adoption</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Don't shop, adopt!</p>
            
            <p><a href="/CVO_Homepage/Adoption" class="btn btn-primary">View Animals For Adoption</a></p>
            <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="$('#modalAdoptionProcess').modal('toggle');">Instruction</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


   <section class="ftco-section cover_1"  data-stellar-background-ratio="0.5" id="learnSection">
      <div class="overlay"></div>
       <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row justify-content-center mb-5 pb-5">
          <div class="col-md-7 text-center heading-section ftco-animate">
            <h2><font color="white">Learn</font></h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row no-gutters ftco-animate">
          <div class="carousel owl-carousel ftco-owl">
           <% function MMMMDDYYYY(i){

                         var days = ['Sunday', 'Monday', 'Tuesday', 'Wednesday', 'Thursday', 'Friday', 'Saturday'];
                         var months = ['January', 'February', 'March', 'April', 'May', 'June', 'July', 'August', 'September', 'October', 'November', 'December'];
                         var now = new Date(i);
                         return months[now.getMonth()] + ' ' + now.getDate() + ', ' + now.getFullYear();
                        
                       } %>
          <% learn.forEach(function(i){ %>
            <div class="item text-center"  style="max-height:480px">
             
                <div class="text">
                 <div class="testimony-wrap p-4 pb-5">
                 <a href="/CVO_Homepage/learn?id=<%= i.int_Learn %>#article" class="block-20" style="background-image: url('/Articles<%= i.str_ImagePath %>');height: 200px">
              </a>
                 <h5><a href="/CVO_Homepage/learn?id=<%= i.int_Learn %>#article"><%= i.str_Topic %></a></h5>
                <div class="meta">
                  <div>Date Posted: <%= MMMMDDYYYY(i.dtm_DateTimePosted) %></div>
                </div>
                <p><%= i.str_Content.slice(0,20)+"..." %></p>
                <p class="clearfix">
                  <a href="/CVO_Homepage/learn?id=<%= i.int_Learn %>#article" class="float-left">Read more..</a>
                </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <% }); %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  
  <!-- Modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="modalRequest" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="modalAppointmentLabel" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header">
            <h5 class="modal-title" id="modalAppointmentLabel">Request a Quote</h5>
            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
              <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-body">
            <form action="#">
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="appointment_name" class="text-black">Full Name</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="appointment_name">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="appointment_email" class="text-black">Email</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="appointment_email">
              </div>
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="appointment_date" class="text-black">Date</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="appointment_date">
                  </div>    
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="appointment_time" class="text-black">Time</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="appointment_time">
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              

              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="appointment_message" class="text-black">Message</label>
                <textarea name="" id="appointment_message" class="form-control" cols="30" rows="10"></textarea>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="submit" value="Send Message" class="btn btn-primary">
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>
          
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
 <!-- Modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="modalRedemptionProcess" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="modalAppointmentLabel" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
